  <body>
    <!-- Navbar starts -->
    {{>navbar}}
    <!-- Navbar ends -->

    <!-- about us section starts -->
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
      <div class="container aboutUs my-5">
        <h1 class="fw-bolder text-center">About <span>us</span></h1>
        <div class="box box-1">
          <img src="../../images/aboutUs/shoe1.jpg" alt="image" width="380px" />
          <div class="description">
            <h2>Our short story</h2>
            <p>
              Welcome to Armenia, where the passion for leather craftsmanship
              thrives. We embarked on this journey with a simple yet powerful
              vision - to bring the experience of genuine leather products to
              everyone in our country. From the finest shoes to stylish belts
              and everyday leather goods, we take pride in curating a collection
              that exudes quality, style, and timeless elegance.
            </p>
            <button class="btn">See more</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="box box-2">
          <div class="description">
            <h2>Our Vision</h2>
            <p>
              At Armenia, our vision is to redefine the way people connect with
              leather products. We believe that everyone deserves to experience
              the unparalleled beauty and craftsmanship of genuine leather. Our
              aim is to create a gateway for our customers to indulge in the
              tactile pleasure, durability, and sophistication that leather
              offers. By bringing together a diverse range of high-quality
              leather goods, we aspire to become the go-to destination for those
              seeking authenticity, style, and an unforgettable sensory
              experience.
            </p>
            <button class="btn">See more</button>
          </div>
          <img src="../../images/aboutUs/shoe2.jpg" alt="image" width="410px" />
        </div>
        <div class="box box-3">
          <img src="../../images/aboutUs/shoe3.jpg" alt="image" width="380px" />
          <div class="description">
            <h2>Our Approach</h2>
            <p>
              At Armenia, we blend tradition and innovation to offer you an
              exceptional shopping experience. Our approach revolves around
              meticulous attention to detail and a deep understanding of our
              customers' desires. We source our leather products from skilled
              artisans who have dedicated their lives to perfecting their craft.
              By collaborating with these talented individuals, we ensure that
              each piece in our collection reflects the passion and expertise
              that goes into its creation. <br /><br />

              Join us on this journey as we invite you to explore our
              meticulously curated collection of leather products. Discover the
              joy of owning something truly exceptional, crafted with love and
              expertise. At Armenia, we strive to go beyond being just a brand â€“
              we aim to be your trusted companion on your quest for unparalleled
              style and the unmistakable allure of leather.
            </p>
            <button class="btn">See more</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- about us section ends -->

    <!-- footer starts -->
    <footer class="footer py-4">
